== Windows and Panes in tmux


   window 0                   window 1                 window 2
 +---------------------+  +--------------------+  +---------------------+
 | pane 0  | pane 1    |  | pane 1             |  | pane 0   | pane 1   |
 |         |           |  |                    |  |          |          |
 |         |           |  |                    |  |          |          |
 |         +-----------|  |                    |  |          |          |
 |         | pane 2    |  |                    |  |          |          |
 |         |           |  |                    |  |__________|__________|
 |         |           |  |                    |  | pane 2              |
 +---------------------+  +--------------------+  +---------------------+



